  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As I said, it was-- I think it was mostly-- the five years of war, or the last three years, at least, from the time we came into the first camp, from the time of Bochnia, where you simply existed.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't think you even hoped for the best.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You simply survived every day, and there was a next day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you never knew what was going to happen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And you were-- I do remember, we were-- we were practically always scared.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I mean, fear was something that-- that was so much part of you that I think that if it disappeared, you'd be terribly surprised, because-- because it was-- it was an intrinsic part of you.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I don't think I-- I think when the war-- I think that it took me time after the war not to be afraid, even though the war was over.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] But I don't really-- I don't even remember many incidents, or any incidents, except for the train thing, and-- oh, silly things like-- [LAUGHS] when the soup used to come in the evening for us to eat, everybody fishing for a-- for a potato or a potato peel-- something that wasn't water.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And then sometimes, I assume Oskar would do that-- getting eggs all of a sudden.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I remember the women beating the eggs up, making a sort of mousse-- [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] --sort of little things-- memories that-- that-- that-- that-- that appear-- from-- so-- from nowhere, but nothing continuous.",
      "word_count": 36
    }
  ],
